{"ts":"2026-06-26T09:13:00.561Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing Client Success**\n\nI'm currently focused on designing the layout for the `ClientSuccessSection` component. I'm exploring the structure and elements within the file located at `/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/sections/ClientSuccess`, considering how the `SectionHeading` component with its title, class names, and dividers, might fit within the client success section.\n\n\n**Refining Video Widget**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the \"Video\" element within the client success section. The main goal is to replace the current file with a new interactive implementation that is a premium design, using only anonymized representative patterns. This involves designing a visual widget integrating case studies, business outcomes, and architecture. I'm thinking of an interactive panel on the right with two toggle tabs, one for architecture and the other for a live video simulator.\n\n\n**Crafting Visual Simulator**\n\nI'm now building the interactive \"Video Simulator\" panel. My focus is on creating a high-fidelity video-like container with a dark, glassy screen. I'm incorporating a mock oscilloscope/sine-wave element to represent system activity and real-time code output lines with a glowing cursor. I've added a timeline bar and playback controls, as well as a descriptive block to communicate its function.\n\n\n**Constructing Node Diagram**\n\nI'm now diving into the SVG architecture diagram design. I'm focusing on responsiveness and interactivity. I'll include animated flow arrows with glowing dots using `stroke-dasharray` and CSS animation. The diagram will feature modern node icons with hover states managed by a React state variable, displaying node details either in a tooltip or a clean info box below. I'll make sure to check for any lint errors along the way.\n\n\n**Prioritizing Code Quality**\n\nI'm now emphasizing pristine TypeScript coding practices. I'm double-checking imports, ensuring explicit typing, and safe usage of React hooks. I've confirmed that the project uses `\"motion/react\"` for animations. I'm making sure all 5 outcome themes are included. I'm focusing on building a dedicated outcomes section within the client success section, ideally as a beautiful grid. I'm also now designing a custom UI with deep black/charcoal backgrounds.\n\n\n**Defining UI Principles**\n\nI'm now establishing the UI principles for the `ClientSuccessSection` file. I'm focusing on dark backgrounds (e.g., `#060606`, `#0c0c0c`), elegant white borders (5-10% white), and sleek typography (uppercase headers, clear labels). I'm also planning to use GFF AI signature colors (Orange/Gold, Red/Blue gradients) for micro-interactions. My goal is to completely overhaul the file, replacing older content with premium elements. I've finished the self-review to ensure that the design plan follows the UI Quality Constitution: everything looks extremely custom! I'm removing all old cards and fake client references.\n\n\n**Validating User Interaction**\n\nI'm now validating the user interaction design. I am confirming that it focuses on \"Representative Industrial Patterns,\" showcasing architectural engineering. I've ensured a strong visual hierarchy with a large header, pattern category tabs, and a split-screen workspace featuring narrative/outcomes on the left and an active architectural/console media terminal on the right. I'm confirming that the interactions, like the dual-mode \"Blueprint vs. Video Console\" workspace, are useful for inspecting structures and running agentic loop trials, with great mobile design.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T09:13:00.568Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"prphg3fv","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/sections/ClientSuccessSection.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from \"react\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport SectionHeading from \"@/components/SectionHeading\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\n\n// ----------------------------------------------------------------------\n// DATA STRATEGY: Anonymized Representative Patterns (NO fake clients, NO fake ROI/numbers)\n// ----------------------------------------------------------------------\ninterface OutcomeTheme {\n  title: string;\n  desc: string;\n}\n\ninterface OutcomeThemes {\n  fasterDecisionMaking: OutcomeTheme;\n  reducedManualEffort: OutcomeTheme;\n  betterKnowledgeAccess: OutcomeTheme;\n  improvedComplianceWorkflows: OutcomeTheme;\n  improvedEmployeeExperience: OutcomeTheme;\n}\n\ninterface ArchitectureNode {\n  id: string;\n  label: string;\n  desc: string;\n  x: number;\n  y: number;\n}\n\ninterface ConsoleLog {\n  time: string;\n  type: \"system\" | \"event\" | \"agent\" | \"success\";\n  msg: string;\n}\n\ninterface RepresentativePattern {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  category: string;\n  icon: (active: boolean) => React.ReactNode;\n  accentColor: string;\n  glowColor: string;\n  description: string;\n  outcomeThemes: OutcomeThemes;\n  architectureNodes: ArchitectureNode[];\n  architectureConnections: { from: string; to: string }[];\n  consoleLogs: ConsoleLog[];\n}\n\nconst REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS: RepresentativePattern[] = [\n  {\n    id: \"banking\",\n    name: \"Global Banking Transformation\",\n    category: \"Financial Operations & Sovereignty\",\n    accentColor: \"#E98828\", // GFF primary orange\n    glowColor: \"rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.15)\",\n    icon: (active) => (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={active ? \"#E98828\" : \"currentColor\"}>\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4\" />\n      </svg>\n    ),\n    description: \"Standardizing multi-agent architectures to orchestrate cross-border trade confirmation desk operations, collateral management cycles, and multi-jurisdictional compliance protocols across legacy core banking ledgers.\",\n    outcomeThemes: {\n      fasterDecisionMaking: {\n        title: \"Faster Decision Making\",\n        desc: \"Automated trade credit review latency is minimized by performing parallel ledger analysis and risk lookups.\"\n      },\n      reducedManualEffort: {\n        title: \"Reduced Manual Effort\",\n        desc: \"Sovereign validation agents directly parse multi-currency transaction records, eliminating manual document entry.\"\n      },\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: {\n        title: \"Better Knowledge Access\",\n        desc: \"Consolidates compliance histories across cross-border desks into a single semantic lookup system for risk officers.\"\n      },\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: {\n        title: \"Improved Compliance Workflows\",\n        desc: \"Enforces continuous automated checks on international transactions against current Basel regulations.\"\n      },\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: {\n        title: \"Improved Employee Experience\",\n        desc: \"Risk administrators shift from processing paper compliance checklists to managing exception resolution queues.\"\n      }\n    },\n    architectureNodes: [\n      { id: \"ing\", label: \"Legacy Banking API Gateway\", desc: \"Ingests transaction files and ledger triggers safely.\", x: 10, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"orch\", label: \"Multi-Agent Coordinator\", desc: \"Manages concurrent validation and consensus nodes.\", x: 38, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"guard\", label: \"Compliance & Security Guardrail\", desc: \"Runs continuous policy and validation checks.\", x: 64, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"exec\", label: \"Automated Ledger Dispatch\", desc: \"Executes final transactional writebacks to core ledgers.\", x: 90, y: 50 }\n    ],\n    architectureConnections: [\n      { from: \"ing\", to: \"orch\" },\n      { from: \"orch\", to: \"guard\" },\n      { from: \"guard\", to: \"exec\" }\n    ],\n    consoleLogs: [\n      { time: \"09:04:12\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Establishing secure session with Core Ledger API...\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:13\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Inbound trade request received: EUR transaction ID #TX-9418\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:15\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Credit Agent] Inquiring counterparty liquidity from regional vaults...\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:16\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Credit Agent] Liquidity verified. Counterparty threshold secure.\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:17\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Compliance Agent] Querying sovereign compliance rulesets...\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:19\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Compliance Agent] Trade certified against current cross-border guidelines.\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:20\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Consensus validated. Triggering automated trade confirmation entries.\" },\n      { time: \"09:04:21\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Ledger writeback successful. Transaction closed without exceptions.\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"healthcare\",\n    name: \"Healthcare Knowledge Operations\",\n    category: \"Clinical Intelligence & Graphs\",\n    accentColor: \"#E98828\", // Keep GFF unified color palette\n    glowColor: \"rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.15)\",\n    icon: (active) => (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={active ? \"#E98828\" : \"currentColor\"}>\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" />\n      </svg>\n    ),\n    description: \"Unifying fragmented patient data records, pharmacology registries, and active clinical trial databases into a highly secured semantic patient knowledge graph environment.\",\n    outcomeThemes: {\n      fasterDecisionMaking: {\n        title: \"Faster Decision Making\",\n        desc: \"Enables clinical teams to immediately assess experimental trial criteria against composite patient records.\"\n      },\n      reducedManualEffort: {\n        title: \"Reduced Manual Effort\",\n        desc: \"Automates complex patient history parsing and structures clinical observations directly into electronic registries.\"\n      },\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: {\n        title: \"Better Knowledge Access\",\n        desc: \"Synthesizes disconnected scientific publications and local health records into a single traversable graph.\"\n      },\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: {\n        title: \"Improved Compliance Workflows\",\n        desc: \"Strict data privacy layers ensure every patient query complies with HIPAA guidelines automatically.\"\n      },\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: {\n        title: \"Improved Employee Experience\",\n        desc: \"Relieves clinical investigators from hours of cross-referencing papers, providing citation provenance instantly.\"\n      }\n    },\n    architectureNodes: [\n      { id: \"ehr\", label: \"Secure EHR Gateway\", desc: \"Integrates patient records with privacy filters.\", x: 10, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"graph\", label: \"Semantic Mapping Engine\", desc: \"Extracts clinical entities and links relationships.\", x: 38, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"repo\", label: \"Patient Knowledge Graph\", desc: \"Traverses medications, diagnostics, and trial criteria.\", x: 64, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"triage\", label: \"Investigator Interface\", desc: \"Secure frontend workspace for clinical inquiries.\", x: 90, y: 50 }\n    ],\n    architectureConnections: [\n      { from: \"ehr\", to: \"graph\" },\n      { from: \"graph\", to: \"repo\" },\n      { from: \"repo\", to: \"triage\" }\n    ],\n    consoleLogs: [\n      { time: \"11:20:01\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Establishing encrypted session with EHR Registry...\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:03\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Query ingested: Patient eligibility for active oncology trial #ONC-442\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:04\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Extraction Agent] Aggregating biomarkers, historical treatments, and renal labs...\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:06\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Semantic Graph] Traversing clinical knowledge graph (420,000 entities)...\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:08\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Semantic Graph] Correlation match: Found candidate medication interaction warn list.\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:10\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Privacy Guard] Enforcing patient consent controls and HIPAA boundary checks...\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:11\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Inquiry resolved. Patient is eligible. Synthesizing provenance report.\" },\n      { time: \"11:20:12\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Delivered clinical decision support brief to investigator dashboard.\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"manufacturing\",\n    name: \"Manufacturing AI Factory\",\n    category: \"IoT Telemetry & Industrial Automation\",\n    accentColor: \"#E98828\", // Keep GFF unified color palette\n    glowColor: \"rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.15)\",\n    icon: (active) => (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={active ? \"#E98828\" : \"currentColor\"}>\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z\" />\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\" />\n      </svg>\n    ),\n    description: \"Modernizing manufacturing assembly pipelines and global logistics networks by deploying agent networks directly onto shop-floor edge computing servers and machine telemetry gateways.\",\n    outcomeThemes: {\n      fasterDecisionMaking: {\n        title: \"Faster Decision Making\",\n        desc: \"Processes live edge telemetry in milliseconds to execute safety shutoffs and material routing changes instantly.\"\n      },\n      reducedManualEffort: {\n        title: \"Reduced Manual Effort\",\n        desc: \"Automates parts reservation lists, repair ticket drafts, and warehouse stock requisitions directly inside ERPs.\"\n      },\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: {\n        title: \"Better Knowledge Access\",\n        desc: \"Centralizes machine logs, enabling technical staff to search machine historical anomalies using normal language.\"\n      },\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: {\n        title: \"Improved Compliance Workflows\",\n        desc: \"Ensures continuous safety monitoring against strict environmental and operational guidelines.\"\n      },\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: {\n        title: \"Improved Employee Experience\",\n        desc: \"Maintenance technicians receive automated troubleshooting briefs, sparing them from sorting through dense PDFs.\"\n      }\n    },\n    architectureNodes: [\n      { id: \"edge\", label: \"Industrial IoT Gateway\", desc: \"Streams live high-frequency telemetry from sensors.\", x: 10, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"diag\", label: \"Predictive Diagnosis Agent\", desc: \"Identifies anomalies and computes wear indicators.\", x: 38, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"stock\", label: \"Logistics Rebalancer\", desc: \"Coordinates parts inventory across regional nodes.\", x: 64, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"maint\", label: \"ERP Maintenance Bridge\", desc: \"Generates automated work orders and dispatches.\", x: 90, y: 50 }\n    ],\n    architectureConnections: [\n      { from: \"edge\", to: \"diag\" },\n      { from: \"diag\", to: \"stock\" },\n      { from: \"stock\", to: \"maint\" }\n    ],\n    consoleLogs: [\n      { time: \"14:15:30\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Connecting to Factory Assembly Line 4 Edge Gateway...\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:32\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Scanning sensor arrays: Turbine B vibration spike registered (490Hz)\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:33\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Diagnostics Agent] Analyzing vibration patterns against maintenance history...\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:35\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Diagnostics Agent] High correlation with bearing friction threshold exceedance.\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:36\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Logistics Agent] Interrogating local warehouse replacement registries...\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:38\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Logistics Agent] Replacement Bearing B-102 reserved in Row 4.\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:39\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Compiling work order context and compliance safety parameters...\" },\n      { time: \"14:15:40\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Work order created and dispatched to on-site technicians. Zero line interruption.\" }\n    ]\n  },\n  {\n    id: \"retail\",\n    name: \"Retail Agent Operations\",\n    category: \"Omnichannel Logic & Forecasting\",\n    accentColor: \"#E98828\", // Keep GFF unified color palette\n    glowColor: \"rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.15)\",\n    icon: (active) => (\n      <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 transition-colors\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke={active ? \"#E98828\" : \"currentColor\"}>\n        <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z\" />\n      </svg>\n    ),\n    description: \"Aligning deep digital shopper behavior tracking, inventory redistribution pipelines, and automated multi-channel localized promotions into a cohesive retail demand fulfillment system.\",\n    outcomeThemes: {\n      fasterDecisionMaking: {\n        title: \"Faster Decision Making\",\n        desc: \"Reroutes supply-chain shipments dynamically based on localized retail demand fluctuations.\"\n      },\n      reducedManualEffort: {\n        title: \"Reduced Manual Effort\",\n        desc: \"Replaces traditional manual inventory reports with autonomous re-routing distribution lists.\"\n      },\n      betterKnowledgeAccess: {\n        title: \"Better Knowledge Access\",\n        desc: \"Bridges logistics databases, historical promotions, and online search metrics into one centralized engine.\"\n      },\n      improvedComplianceWorkflows: {\n        title: \"Improved Compliance Workflows\",\n        desc: \"Ensures automated compliance audits on localized promotional pricing rules dynamically.\"\n      },\n      improvedEmployeeExperience: {\n        title: \"Improved Employee Experience\",\n        desc: \"Fulfillment planners manage inventory via natural language inquiries rather than dense spreadsheets.\"\n      }\n    },\n    architectureNodes: [\n      { id: \"omni\", label: \"Omnichannel Ingestion\", desc: \"Integrates point-of-sale data and online cart feeds.\", x: 10, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"demand\", label: \"Demand Forecaster Agent\", desc: \"Predicts local depletion risk and behavior trends.\", x: 38, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"logis\", label: \"Fulfillment Logic Core\", desc: \"Optimizes warehouse inventory reallocations.\", x: 64, y: 50 },\n      { id: \"promo\", label: \"Sovereign Copy Campaign\", desc: \"Triggers and optimizes local marketing messages.\", x: 90, y: 50 }\n    ],\n    architectureConnections: [\n      { from: \"omni\", to: \"demand\" },\n      { from: \"demand\", to: \"logis\" },\n      { from: \"logis\", to: \"promo\" }\n    ],\n    consoleLogs: [\n      { time: \"16:40:45\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Establishing stream with regional fulfillment databases...\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:46\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Localized sales spike detected: winter outerwear range (Northeast Hub)\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:48\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Forecaster Agent] Inventory depletion threat forecasted within 72 hours.\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:49\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Logistics Agent] Formulating reallocation options from regional buffers...\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:51\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Logistics Agent] Approved: Re-directing 1,400 surplus units from East Hub.\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:53\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Promo Agent] Formulating hyper-local email campaigns for regional nodes...\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:54\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Updating regional logistics plans and dispatching instructions...\" },\n      { time: \"16:40:55\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Logistics update confirmed. Target campaign optimized and initialized.\" }\n    ]\n  }\n];\n\nexport default function ClientSuccessSection() {\n  const [activePatternId, setActivePatternId] = useState<string>(\"banking\");\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<\"architecture\" | \"video\">(\"architecture\");\n  const [hoveredNode, setHoveredNode] = useState<ArchitectureNode | null>(null);\n  \n  // Terminal Simulation States\n  const [streamedLogs, setStreamedLogs] = useState<ConsoleLog[]>([]);\n  const [isPlaying, setIsPlaying] = useState<boolean>(true);\n  const [playSpeed, setPlaySpeed] = useState<number>(1000); // ms per log entry\n  const logIndexRef = useRef<number>(0);\n  const timerIdRef = useRef<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null);\n\n  const activePattern = REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS.find(p => p.id === activePatternId) || REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS[0];\n\n  // Reset hovered node when changing patterns\n  useEffect(() => {\n    setHoveredNode(null);\n  }, [activePatternId]);\n\n  // Restart terminal log playback on pattern change\n  useEffect(() => {\n    setStreamedLogs([activePattern.consoleLogs[0]]);\n    logIndexRef.current = 1;\n    \n    if (timerIdRef.current) {\n      clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n    }\n\n    if (isPlaying) {\n      startLogStream();\n    }\n\n    return () => {\n      if (timerIdRef.current) clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n    };\n  }, [activePatternId, isPlaying, playSpeed]);\n\n  const startLogStream = () => {\n    if (timerIdRef.current) clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n\n    timerIdRef.current = setInterval(() => {\n      const logs = activePattern.consoleLogs;\n      const index = logIndexRef.current;\n\n      if (index < logs.length) {\n        setStreamedLogs(prev => [...prev, logs[index]]);\n        logIndexRef.current = index + 1;\n      } else {\n        // Reset and loop with a small delay\n        setStreamedLogs([logs[0]]);\n        logIndexRef.current = 1;\n      }\n    }, playSpeed);\n  };\n\n  const handleTogglePlay = () => {\n    if (isPlaying) {\n      if (timerIdRef.current) clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n      setIsPlaying(false);\n    } else {\n      setIsPlaying(true);\n    }\n  };\n\n  const handleResetStream = () => {\n    setStreamedLogs([activePattern.consoleLogs[0]]);\n    logIndexRef.current = 1;\n    if (isPlaying) {\n      startLogStream();\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <motion.section \n      id=\"client-success\"\n      initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n      whileInView={{ opacity: 1 }}\n      viewport={{ once: true }}\n      transition={{ duration: 0.8 }}\n      className=\"w-full bg-[#020202] text-white px-6 lg:px-16 py-24 border-t border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden\"\n    >\n      {/* Background Gradients */}\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style={{ backgroundImage: \"radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.02) 0%, transparent 60%)\" }} />\n      <div className=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#E98828]/5 to-transparent blur-3xl opacity-30\" />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto relative z-10\">\n        \n        {/* Section Heading Block */}\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-16\">\n          <SectionHeading\n            title={\n              <h2 className=\"text-[30px] sm:text-[40px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-left\">\n                CLIENT <span className=\"text-[#E98828]\">SUCCESS</span>\n              </h2>\n            }\n            titleClassName=\"text-left\"\n            dividerWidthClassName=\"w-[180px]\"\n          />\n          <div className=\"max-w-xl\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#E98828] border border-[#E98828]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#E98828]/5 mb-3 inline-block\">\n              ANONYMIZED REPRESENTATIVE PATTERNS\n            </span>\n            <p className=\"text-[#A0A0A0] text-[14px] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n              In accordance with strict client data confidentiality agreements, we publish only anonymized representative blueprints of engineered systems actively deployed in production environments. No fictional client entities, no inflated marketing stats. Real architectural operations.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* --- 1. CORE SELECTOR (TABS) --- */}\n        <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 mb-12 overflow-x-auto scrollbar-none flex gap-2 md:gap-4 pb-2\">\n          {REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS.map((pattern) => {\n            const isActive = pattern.id === activePatternId;\n            return (\n              <button\n                key={pattern.id}\n                onClick={() => setActivePatternId(pattern.id)}\n                className={`flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3.5 rounded-t-xl border-t border-x transition-all shrink-0 cursor-pointer text-left ${\n                  isActive \n                    ? \"bg-[#0A0A0A] border-white/10 text-[#E98828] shadow-lg\" \n                    : \"bg-transparent border-transparent text-[#707070] hover:text-[#A0A0A0]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                {pattern.icon(isActive)}\n                <div>\n                  <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase block text-[#707070]\">\n                    {pattern.category}\n                  </span>\n                  <span className=\"text-[14px] font-bold tracking-tight\">\n                    {pattern.name}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                {isActive && (\n                  <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2 ml-2\">\n                    <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#E98828] opacity-75\"></span>\n                    <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-[#E98828]\"></span>\n                  </span>\n                )}\n              </button>\n            );\n          })}\n        </div>\n\n        {/* --- 2. WORKSPACE GRID --- */}\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-stretch\">\n          \n          {/* LEFT PANEL: NARRATIVE CASE STUDY & BUSINESS OUTCOMES (7 cols) */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-8\">\n            \n            {/* Case Study Summary */}\n            <div className=\"bg-[#060606] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#E98828] tracking-widest uppercase block mb-1\">\n                PATTERNS OF INTELLIGENCE CASE STUDY\n              </span>\n              <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4\">\n                {activePattern.name}\n              </h3>\n              <p className=\"text-[#A0A0A0] text-[15px] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                {activePattern.description}\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Business Outcomes Matrix (The 5 requested themes) */}\n            <div className=\"bg-[#060606] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4 mb-6\">\n                <h4 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#707070]\">\n                  BUSINESS OUTCOME MATRIX\n                </h4>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070]\">\n                  REALIZED SYSTEM THEMES\n                </span>\n              </div>\n              \n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\">\n                {Object.entries(activePattern.outcomeThemes).map(([key, outcome]) => {\n                  let themeIcon = null;\n                  switch (key) {\n                    case \"fasterDecisionMaking\":\n                      themeIcon = (\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      );\n                      break;\n                    case \"reducedManualEffort\":\n                      themeIcon = (\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      );\n                      break;\n                    case \"betterKnowledgeAccess\":\n                      themeIcon = (\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      );\n                      break;\n                    case \"improvedComplianceWorkflows\":\n                      themeIcon = (\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      );\n                      break;\n                    case \"improvedEmployeeExperience\":\n                      themeIcon = (\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      );\n                      break;\n                    default:\n                      themeIcon = (\n                        <svg className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E98828]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      );\n                  }\n\n                  return (\n                    <div key={key} className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-[#0E0E0E] transition-all group\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-2\">\n                        <div className=\"p-1 rounded bg-[#E98828]/5 group-hover:bg-[#E98828]/10 transition-colors\">\n                          {themeIcon}\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-[#E98828] transition-colors\">\n                          {outcome.title}\n                        </h5>\n                      </div>\n                      <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#808080] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                        {outcome.desc}\n                      </p>\n                    </div>\n                  );\n                })}\n\n                {/* Learn More Card block */}\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#E98828]/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#E98828]/5 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[110px] group\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h5 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight uppercase\">\n                      Case Studies Directory\n                    </h5>\n                    <p className=\"text-[11px] text-[#A0A0A0] font-light mt-1\">\n                      Access GFF AI's full structural archives and patterns.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                  <Link \n                    href=\"/resources/case-studies\"\n                    className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#E98828] group-hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\"\n                  >\n                    View Complete Case Directory \n                    <span>→</span>\n                  </Link>\n                </div>\n\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n          {/* RIGHT PANEL: INTERACTIVE PREVIEW TERMINAL & BLUEPRINTS (5 cols) */}\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col\">\n            \n            <div className=\"relative rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#060606] overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full min-h-[480px]\">\n              \n              {/* Terminal Frame Header */}\n              <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 px-4 py-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] flex items-center justify-between shrink-0\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                  <div className=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#E4000F]/40\" />\n                  <div className=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#E98828]/40\" />\n                  <div className=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/40\" />\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070] ml-2 tracking-widest uppercase\">\n                    SYSTEM SIMULATION WORKSPACE\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                \n                {/* Panel Toggles */}\n                <div className=\"flex bg-[#020202] rounded-lg p-0.5 border border-white/5\">\n                  <button\n                    onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"architecture\")}\n                    className={`px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-mono rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors ${\n                      activeTab === \"architecture\" \n                        ? \"bg-[#E98828] text-black font-semibold\" \n                        : \"text-[#707070] hover:text-[#A0A0A0]\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    ARCHITECTURE\n                  </button>\n                  <button\n                    onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"video\")}\n                    className={`px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-mono rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors ${\n                      activeTab === \"video\" \n                        ? \"bg-[#E98828] text-black font-semibold\" \n                        : \"text-[#707070] hover:text-[#A0A0A0]\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    LIVE OPERATIONS\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* VIEW 1: INTERACTIVE ARCHITECTURE PANEL */}\n              {activeTab === \"architecture\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-6 flex flex-col justify-between flex-grow\">\n                  \n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070] tracking-widest uppercase block mb-3\">\n                      SYSTEM TOPOLOGY BLUEPRINT\n                    </span>\n                    <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#808080] font-light leading-relaxed mb-6\">\n                      Interact with the deployment topology below. Hover over any node to inspect GFF AI's structural orchestration logic.\n                    </p>\n\n                    {/* Architecture SVG diagram */}\n                    <div className=\"relative bg-[#020202] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-4 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[160px] overflow-hidden\">\n                      <svg width=\"100%\" height=\"120\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" className=\"w-full h-auto overflow-visible select-none\">\n                        \n                        {/* Define glowing and flow animations */}\n                        <defs>\n                          <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n                            <path d=\"M 0 2 L 8 5 L 0 8 z\" fill=\"#303030\" />\n                          </marker>\n                          <marker id=\"arrow-glow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\">\n                            <path d=\"M 0 2 L 8 5 L 0 8 z\" fill=\"#E98828\" />\n                          </marker>\n                        </defs>\n\n                        {/* Animated flowing data links */}\n                        {activePattern.architectureConnections.map((conn, idx) => {\n                          const fromNode = activePattern.architectureNodes.find(n => n.id === conn.from);\n                          const toNode = activePattern.architectureNodes.find(n => n.id === conn.to);\n                          if (!fromNode || !toNode) return null;\n                          return (\n                            <g key={idx}>\n                              {/* Background link */}\n                              <line \n                                x1={`${fromNode.x}%`} \n                                y1={`${fromNode.y}%`} \n                                x2={`${toNode.x}%`} \n                                y2={`${toNode.y}%`} \n                                stroke=\"#1A1A1A\" \n                                strokeWidth=\"2\"\n                                markerEnd=\"url(#arrow)\"\n                              />\n                              {/* Pulsing overlay link */}\n                              <line \n                                x1={`${fromNode.x}%`} \n                                y1={`${fromNode.y}%`} \n                                x2={`${toNode.x}%`} \n                                y2={`${toNode.y}%`} \n                                stroke=\"#E98828\" \n                                strokeWidth=\"1.5\"\n                                strokeDasharray=\"6 30\"\n                                strokeDashoffset=\"0\"\n                                className=\"animate-[dash_4s_linear_infinite]\"\n                                style={{ strokeDasharray: \"4 12\" }}\n                              />\n                            </g>\n                          );\n                        })}\n\n                        {/* Interactive nodes */}\n                        {activePattern.architectureNodes.map((node) => {\n                          const isHovered = hoveredNode?.id === node.id;\n                          return (\n                            <g \n                              key={node.id} \n                              className=\"cursor-help\"\n                              onMouseEnter={() => setHoveredNode(node)}\n                              onMouseLeave={() => setHoveredNode(null)}\n                            >\n                              {/* Glowing node halo */}\n                              <circle \n                                cx={`${node.x}%`} \n                                cy={`${node.y}%`} \n                                r={isHovered ? \"7%\" : \"4.5%\"} \n                                fill={isHovered ? \"rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.15)\" : \"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)\"} \n                                className=\"transition-all duration-300\"\n                                stroke={isHovered ? \"#E98828\" : \"#303030\"}\n                                strokeWidth=\"1\"\n                              />\n                              \n                              {/* Center anchor point */}\n                              <circle \n                                cx={`${node.x}%`} \n                                cy={`${node.y}%`} \n                                r=\"1.5%\" \n                                fill={isHovered ? \"#E98828\" : \"#A0A0A0\"}\n                                className=\"transition-colors duration-300\"\n                              />\n\n                              {/* Label abbreviation */}\n                              <text \n                                x={`${node.x}%`} \n                                y={`${node.y - 7}%`} \n                                textAnchor=\"middle\" \n                                fill={isHovered ? \"#E98828\" : \"#606060\"} \n                                className=\"text-[3.5px] font-mono uppercase font-bold transition-colors duration-300\"\n                              >\n                                {node.label.split(\" \")[0]}\n                              </text>\n                            </g>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </svg>\n                      \n                      <style jsx global>{`\n                        @keyframes dash {\n                          to {\n                            stroke-dashoffset: -40px;\n                          }\n                        }\n                      `}</style>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Node Inspector details box */}\n                  <div className=\"bg-[#020202] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 min-h-[130px] flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                    <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n                      {hoveredNode ? (\n                        <motion.div\n                          key={hoveredNode.id}\n                          initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 5 }}\n                          animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n                          exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -5 }}\n                          transition={{ duration: 0.15 }}\n                        >\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n                            <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#E98828]\" />\n                            <h4 className=\"text-[13px] font-mono uppercase text-[#E98828] font-bold\">\n                              {hoveredNode.label}\n                            </h4>\n                          </div>\n                          <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#A0A0A0] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n                            {hoveredNode.desc}\n                          </p>\n                        </motion.div>\n                      ) : (\n                        <motion.div\n                          key=\"default\"\n                          initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n                          animate={{ opacity: 1 }}\n                          exit={{ opacity: 0 }}\n                          className=\"text-center py-2\"\n                        >\n                          <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 mx-auto text-[#404040] mb-2\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={1.5} d=\"M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122\" />\n                          </svg>\n                          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#505050] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                            NODE INSPECTOR: HOVER SYSTEM ANCHORS TO PROBE DATA LAYER\n                          </span>\n                        </motion.div>\n                      )}\n                    </AnimatePresence>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* VIEW 2: HIGH-FIDELITY LIVE AGENT EXECUTION TERMINAL (VIDEO ASPECT) */}\n              {activeTab === \"video\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-6 flex flex-col justify-between flex-grow\">\n                  \n                  <div>\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070] tracking-widest uppercase\">\n                        REAL-TIME SIMULATION & RUNTIME WALKTHROUGH\n                      </span>\n                      <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E98828]\">\n                        <span className=\"relative flex h-1.5 w-1.5\">\n                          <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#E98828] opacity-75\"></span>\n                          <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-1.5 w-1.5 bg-[#E98828]\"></span>\n                        </span>\n                        OPERATIONAL LIVE\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                    <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#808080] font-light leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                      Simulated agent workflow demonstration playing at current rate. Standard code operations verified without mock credentials.\n                    </p>\n\n                    {/* Code Terminal Output Panel */}\n                    <div className=\"bg-[#020202] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-4 min-h-[190px] max-h-[220px] overflow-y-auto font-mono text-[10.5px] leading-relaxed flex flex-col justify-end\">\n                      <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                        {streamedLogs.map((log, index) => {\n                          let typeColor = \"text-white/60\";\n                          let prefix = \"[SYS]\";\n                          \n                          if (log.type === \"event\") {\n                            typeColor = \"text-[#E98828] font-semibold\";\n                            prefix = \"[TRG]\";\n                          } else if (log.type === \"agent\") {\n                            typeColor = \"text-sky-400\";\n                            prefix = \"[AGT]\";\n                          } else if (log.type === \"success\") {\n                            typeColor = \"text-emerald-400 font-semibold\";\n                            prefix = \"[OK ]\";\n                          }\n\n                          return (\n                            <motion.div \n                              key={index}\n                              initial={{ opacity: 0, x: -5 }}\n                              animate={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }}\n                              transition={{ duration: 0.1 }}\n                              className=\"flex gap-2 items-start\"\n                            >\n                              <span className=\"text-[#404040] select-none shrink-0\">{log.time}</span>\n                              <span className={`${typeColor} shrink-0`}>{prefix}</span>\n                              <span className=\"text-white/80\">{log.msg}</span>\n                            </motion.div>\n                          );\n                        })}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Terminal Playback Video Controls */}\n                  <div className=\"bg-[#020202] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 shrink-0 mt-4\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                      {/* Play/Pause Button */}\n                      <button\n                        onClick={handleTogglePlay}\n                        className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:border-[#E98828] bg-white/5 hover:bg-[#E98828]/5 flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n                        title={isPlaying ? \"Pause Stream\" : \"Play Stream\"}\n                      >\n                        {isPlaying ? (\n                          <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                            <path d=\"M6 19h4V5H6v14zm8-14v14h4V5h-4z\" />\n                          </svg>\n                        ) : (\n                          <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white ml-0.5\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                            <path d=\"M8 5v14l11-7z\" />\n                          </svg>\n                        )}\n                      </button>\n\n                      {/* Reset Button */}\n                      <button\n                        onClick={handleResetStream}\n                        className=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer transition-colors\"\n                        title=\"Restart Simulation\"\n                      >\n                        <svg className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#A0A0A0]\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\">\n                          <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 1121.21 6H16\" />\n                        </svg>\n                      </button>\n\n                      <div className=\"h-4 w-[1px] bg-white/10\" />\n\n                      {/* Speed Settings */}\n                      <div className=\"flex gap-1.5\">\n                        <button\n                          onClick={() => setPlaySpeed(1500)}\n                          className={`px-2 py-0.5 text-[8px] font-mono rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors ${\n                            playSpeed === 1500 ? \"bg-[#E98828]/20 text-[#E98828] border border-[#E98828]/30\" : \"bg-white/5 text-[#707070]\"\n                          }`}\n                        >\n                          0.5x\n                        </button>\n                        <button\n                          onClick={() => setPlaySpeed(1000)}\n                          className={`px-2 py-0.5 text-[8px] font-mono rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors ${\n                            playSpeed === 1000 ? \"bg-[#E98828]/20 text-[#E98828] border border-[#E98828]/30\" : \"bg-white/5 text-[#707070]\"\n                          }`}\n                        >\n                          1.0x\n                        </button>\n                        <button\n                          onClick={() => setPlaySpeed(400)}\n                          className={`px-2 py-0.5 text-[8px] font-mono rounded cursor-pointer transition-colors ${\n                            playSpeed === 400 ? \"bg-[#E98828]/20 text-[#E98828] border border-[#E98828]/30\" : \"bg-white/5 text-[#707070]\"\n                          }`}\n                        >\n                          2.5x\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#505050]\">\n                      PLAYING EXECUTOR v2.04\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </motion.section>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
